@Meta date:2026-07-14

@Chg:AsyncDBSetup [scope:quado-desktop]
Ctx: UI startup freeze → blocking operations → move to background threads → responsive UI
Act:
- upd:DashboardController.pathFieldListener [logic:CompletableFuture.runAsync() for project switch]
- upd:ArcadeDbService.initializeProjectDatabase [logic:runAsync background]
- upd:ArcadeDbService.refreshStats [logic:runAsync background]
- upd:MainController.notifyPathChanged [logic:Platform.runLater()]
- rm:duplicateDBInitCalls

@Chg:SchemaCacheVerification [scope:ArcadeDbService]
Ctx: repeated CREATE PROPERTY/INDEX queries on startup → parser overhead → in-memory cache first
Act:
- upd:ArcadeDbService.schemaCheck [logic:memory cache (existsProperty, getPolymorphicIndexByProperties)]
- cr:SQLCommand [cond:property or index missing]
- result: 0 schema setup queries on subsequent startups

@Chg:LazyStrategyIndexers [scope:CodeIndexerService]
Ctx: eager @Component loading all indexers → >200MB Metaspace + GC pressure → lazy load on demand
Act:
- rm:@Component [target:JavaIndexer|GoIndexer|PythonIndexer|TypeScriptIndexer|VueIndexer|DelphiIndexer|SqlIndexer]
- cr:indexerRegistry [target:CodeIndexerService, logic:thread-safe Supplier<Indexer>]
- defer:loadIndexer [cond:first file with matching extension]
- effect: unused language parsers not loaded

@Chg:AccurateFQNCallGraph [scope:JavaIndexer]
Ctx: short method name CALLS edges → false positives (getName, run...) → FQN + import resolution
Act:
- cr:MethodVertex [logic:FQN pattern = packageName.ClassName.methodSignature]
- upd:receiverResolution [logic:local var types + imports → fullClassName]
- upd:CALLSEdgeCreation [cond:receiver type resolvable]
- rm:fallbackNameOnlyMatching
- note: other languages accept unresolved receiver (no edge)

@Chg:GraphViewerFilter [scope:GraphController]
Ctx: Function→Function edges → visual clutter in Graph Viewer
Act:
- upd:CypherQueries [target:loadGraphVisualization|search|expandNode, logic:AND NOT (a:Function AND b:Function)]
- result: only Type→Function and Type↔Type dependencies shown

@Chg:RelativePathStorage [scope:AllIndexers]
Ctx: absolute file paths in DB → break on project move → store relative to project root
Act:
- upd:filepathStorage [logic:SourceCodeIndexer.toRelativePathStr(file, projectRoot)]
- upd:hashKeys [target:currentHashes|previousHashes, logic:relative path]
- defer:absolutePathResolution [target:SummaryEngineImpl|AiAnalysisService, logic:graphDbService.resolveToAbsolutePath()]
- effect: project copy/move without re-indexing